# Smoke Test Cases

## TC-SMOKE-001: New user mobile registration

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| **ID** | TC-SMOKE-001 |
| **Priority** | 1 (Smoke) |
| **Requirement** | REQ1 |
| **Module** | User Registration |
| **Title** | Mobile phone registration |

**Test Steps:**
1. Open website on mobile device
2. Enter phone number in "Mobile" field
3. Wait for SMS with code
4. Enter code in verification field
5. Click "Registration" button

**Expected Results:**
1. Website loads successfully
2. Phone number displays in "Mobile" field
3. SMS code received on phone number
4. Code displays in verification field
5. Success registration message appears

